<h4 data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: bold; color: black; font-size: 18px;"><span class="prefix" style="display: none;"></span><span class="content">在linux系统上安装所需的依赖：ssh，防火墙， postfix，wget。</span><span class="suffix" style="display: none;"></span></h4>
<ol data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 25px; color: black; list-style-type: decimal;">
